<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>مخطط نظام المطعم</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@400;600;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
/* ═══ RESET & BASE ═══ */
*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
:root {
  --gold: #c9a84c;
  --gold2: #e8d49a;
  --bg: #0d1018;
  --bg2: #13171f;
  --bg3: #1a1e2a;
  --muted: #8a8070;
  --text: #ddd8cc;
  --hot: #c0392b;
  --grill: #e67e22;
  --fry: #d35400;
  --cold: #2980b9;
  --pastry: #8e44ad;
  --bar: #16a085;
  --green: #27ae60;
  --teal: #17a2b8;
}
body {
  font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  direction: rtl;
  padding: 20px;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

/* ═══ PAGE HEADER ═══ */
.page-title {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.page-title h1 {
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: var(--gold);
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}
.page-title p {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin-top: 4px;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
}

/* ═══ SECTION LABEL ═══ */
.section-label {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gold);
  letter-spacing: 4px;
  opacity: 0.7;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* ═══ ARROW ═══ */
.arrow-down {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  height: 28px;
  color: var(--gold);
  font-size: 18px;
  opacity: 0.7;
}
.arrow-down-dashed {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  height: 24px;
  position: relative;
}
.arrow-down-dashed::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; bottom: 0;
  width: 2px;
  border-right: 2px dashed rgba(201,168,76,0.4);
}
.arrow-down-dashed::after {
  content: '▼';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  color: var(--gold);
  font-size: 10px;
  opacity: 0.6;
}

/* ═══ CHANNELS ROW ═══ */
.channels-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
  gap: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.channel-card {
  background: var(--bg3);
  border: 1.5px solid;
  border-radius: 10px;
  overflow: hidden;
  font-size: 12px;
}
.channel-header {
  padding: 7px 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 13px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
}
.channel-body {
  padding: 6px 10px 8px;
}
.channel-body p {
  font-size: 10px;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin-bottom: 2px;
}

/* Waiter app highlight */
.channel-waiter {
  border-color: var(--green) !important;
  box-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(39,174,96,0.25);
  position: relative;
}
.channel-waiter .channel-header {
  background: rgba(39,174,96,0.15);
  color: #2ecc71;
}
.waiter-badge {
  position: absolute;
  top: -6px;
  left: -6px;
  background: #2ecc71;
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 900;
  border-radius: 50%;
  width: 22px;
  height: 22px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
}

/* ═══ FUNNEL CONNECTOR ═══ */
.funnel-wrap {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  position: relative;
  height: 32px;
  margin: 0;
}
.funnel-line {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 8.3%; right: 8.3%;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(201,168,76,0.5), transparent);
}
.funnel-arrow {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
}
.funnel-arrow::before {
  content: '';
  width: 2px;
  height: 24px;
  background: rgba(201,168,76,0.6);
}
.funnel-arrow::after {
  content: '▼';
  color: var(--gold);
  font-size: 10px;
  line-height: 1;
}

/* ═══ ORDER ENGINE ═══ */
.engine-wrap {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.engine-box {
  background: rgba(201,168,76,0.07);
  border: 2px solid var(--gold);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 10px 24px;
  text-align: center;
  width: 680px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
}
.engine-box h3 {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: var(--gold2);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.engine-box .lifecycle {
  font-size: 10px;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin-bottom: 3px;
  direction: ltr;
  text-align: center;
}
.engine-box .tags {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 5px;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-top: 5px;
}
.etag {
  background: rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.25);
  color: var(--gold);
  font-size: 9px;
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 10px;
}

/* ═══ KITCHEN GRID ═══ */
.kitchen-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.station-card {
  border-radius: 11px;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1.8px solid;
}
.station-header {
  padding: 8px 12px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}
.station-header-inner { flex: 1; }
.station-title {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 700;
}
.station-subtitle {
  font-size: 9px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  margin-top: 1px;
}
.kds-badge {
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
  border: 1px solid currentColor;
  border-radius: 5px;
  padding: 3px 7px;
  font-size: 9px;
  font-weight: 700;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

/* Prep store */
.prep-store {
  margin: 8px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  border: 1.2px solid;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.prep-store-header {
  padding: 5px 10px;
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 5px;
}
.prep-store-body {
  padding: 6px 10px 8px;
}
.bom-label {
  font-size: 9px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.bom-item {
  font-size: 9px;
  color: #aaa;
  padding: 2px 0;
  padding-right: 10px;
  position: relative;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
.bom-item::before {
  content: '◈';
  position: absolute;
  right: 0;
  color: rgba(201,168,76,0.5);
  font-size: 8px;
  top: 3px;
}
.supply-note {
  font-size: 8.5px;
  color: var(--teal);
  margin-top: 5px;
  padding-top: 5px;
  border-top: 1px dashed rgba(23,162,184,0.2);
  text-align: center;
}

/* ═══ HOT STATION ═══ */
.st-hot { border-color: var(--hot); background: #170a0a; }
.st-hot .station-header { background: rgba(192,57,43,0.25); color: #f1948a; }
.st-hot .prep-store { border-color: rgba(192,57,43,0.35); background: rgba(192,57,43,0.04); }
.st-hot .prep-store-header { background: rgba(192,57,43,0.12); color: var(--hot); }
.st-hot .kds-badge { color: #f1948a; }

/* ═══ GRILL STATION ═══ */
.st-grill { border-color: var(--grill); background: #170e05; }
.st-grill .station-header { background: rgba(230,126,34,0.22); color: #f5cba7; }
.st-grill .prep-store { border-color: rgba(230,126,34,0.35); background: rgba(230,126,34,0.04); }
.st-grill .prep-store-header { background: rgba(230,126,34,0.12); color: var(--grill); }
.st-grill .kds-badge { color: #f5cba7; }

/* ═══ FRY STATION ═══ */
.st-fry { border-color: var(--fry); background: #160d05; }
.st-fry .station-header { background: rgba(211,84,0,0.25); color: #f0b27a; }
.st-fry .prep-store { border-color: rgba(211,84,0,0.35); background: rgba(211,84,0,0.04); }
.st-fry .prep-store-header { background: rgba(211,84,0,0.12); color: var(--fry); }
.st-fry .kds-badge { color: #f0b27a; }

/* ═══ COLD STATION ═══ */
.st-cold { border-color: var(--cold); background: #070f18; }
.st-cold .station-header { background: rgba(41,128,185,0.22); color: #aed6f1; }
.st-cold .prep-store { border-color: rgba(41,128,185,0.35); background: rgba(41,128,185,0.04); }
.st-cold .prep-store-header { background: rgba(41,128,185,0.12); color: var(--cold); }
.st-cold .kds-badge { color: #aed6f1; }

/* ═══ PASTRY STATION ═══ */
.st-pastry { border-color: var(--pastry); background: #0d0812; }
.st-pastry .station-header { background: rgba(142,68,173,0.22); color: #d7bde2; }
.st-pastry .prep-store { border-color: rgba(142,68,173,0.35); background: rgba(142,68,173,0.04); }
.st-pastry .prep-store-header { background: rgba(142,68,173,0.12); color: var(--pastry); }
.st-pastry .kds-badge { color: #d7bde2; }

/* ═══ BAR STATION ═══ */
.st-bar { border-color: var(--bar); background: #050f0d; }
.st-bar .station-header { background: rgba(22,160,133,0.22); color: #a2d9ce; }
.st-bar .prep-store { border-color: rgba(22,160,133,0.35); background: rgba(22,160,133,0.04); }
.st-bar .prep-store-header { background: rgba(22,160,133,0.12); color: var(--bar); }
.st-bar .kds-badge { color: #a2d9ce; }

/* ═══ EXPO ═══ */
.expo-wrap {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.expo-box {
  background: rgba(201,168,76,0.06);
  border: 2px solid var(--gold);
  border-radius: 11px;
  padding: 10px 28px;
  text-align: center;
  width: 620px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(201,168,76,0.08);
}
.expo-box h3 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold2); margin-bottom: 3px; }
.expo-box p { font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); }

/* ═══ OUTPUT ROW ═══ */
.output-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 12px;
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto 6px;
}
.output-card {
  border-radius: 10px;
  border: 1.5px solid;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.output-header {
  padding: 7px 14px;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 700;
}
.output-body {
  padding: 6px 14px 8px;
}
.output-body p { font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2px; }

.out-dinein { border-color: var(--gold); background: #12110a; }
.out-dinein .output-header { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.14); color: var(--gold2); }
.out-delivery { border-color: var(--grill); background: #100c06; }
.out-delivery .output-header { background: rgba(230,126,34,0.14); color: #f5cba7; }

/* ═══ WAREHOUSE ═══ */
.warehouse-box {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0c1820, #07101a);
  border: 2px solid var(--teal);
  border-radius: 12px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-top: 6px;
}
.warehouse-header {
  background: rgba(23,162,184,0.1);
  padding: 10px 20px;
  text-align: center;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(23,162,184,0.15);
}
.warehouse-header h3 {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: #7ecfdb;
  margin-bottom: 3px;
}
.warehouse-header p { font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); }
.warehouse-zones {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 10px;
}
.zone {
  border-radius: 8px;
  border: 1.2px solid;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.zone-header {
  padding: 6px 10px;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-align: center;
}
.zone-body {
  padding: 6px 10px 8px;
}
.zone-body p { font-size: 9.5px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2px; }
.zone-body small { font-size: 8.5px; color: #5a5048; }

.zone-dry { border-color: rgba(241,196,15,0.25); background: rgba(241,196,15,0.04); }
.zone-dry .zone-header { background: rgba(241,196,15,0.1); color: #f1c40f; }
.zone-chill { border-color: rgba(41,128,185,0.25); background: rgba(41,128,185,0.04); }
.zone-chill .zone-header { background: rgba(41,128,185,0.12); color: #aed6f1; }
.zone-frozen { border-color: rgba(52,152,219,0.22); background: rgba(52,152,219,0.04); }
.zone-frozen .zone-header { background: rgba(52,152,219,0.1); color: #85c1e9; }

/* ═══ SUPPLY ARROWS ═══ */
.supply-arrows-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 10px;
  margin: 0 0 0;
}
.supply-col {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 4px 0 2px;
}
.supply-col span {
  font-size: 8px;
  color: var(--teal);
  opacity: 0.75;
  margin-bottom: 2px;
}
.supply-arrow-line {
  width: 2px;
  height: 20px;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(23,162,184,0.5));
  position: relative;
}
.supply-arrow-line::after {
  content: '▲';
  position: absolute;
  top: -8px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  color: var(--teal);
  font-size: 8px;
  opacity: 0.7;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="page-title">
  <h1>🍽 مخطط نظام تشغيل المطعم الاحترافي</h1>
  <p>قنوات الطلب ← محرك الطلبات ← المطابخ الفرعية + مخازن التحضير ← المخزن الرئيسي</p>
</div>

<!-- ═══ قنوات الطلب ═══ -->
<div class="section-label">— قنوات الطلب —</div>
<div class="channels-row">

  <!-- 1. POS -->
  <div class="channel-card" style="border-color:#6c3db5; background:#14102a;">
    <div class="channel-header" style="background:rgba(108,61,181,0.2); color:#c3aee8;">
      🖥 نقطة البيع POS
    </div>
    <div class="channel-body">
      <p>تقسيم فاتورة • كوبونات</p>
      <p>Offline • Loyalty ربط</p>
      <p>EMV • Apple Pay • Mada</p>
      <p>كورسينج • معدّلات</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 2. Waiter App ★ -->
  <div class="channel-card channel-waiter" style="background:#0c1a0c;">
    <div class="waiter-badge">★</div>
    <div class="channel-header">
      📲 تطبيق النادل
    </div>
    <div class="channel-body">
      <p style="color:#a9dfbf;">Waiter / Server App</p>
      <p>خريطة طاولات لحظية</p>
      <p>تحديث 86 فوري</p>
      <p>طلب حسب المقعد • Recall</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 3. Kiosk -->
  <div class="channel-card" style="border-color:#27ae60; background:#0c1a0c;">
    <div class="channel-header" style="background:rgba(39,174,96,0.18); color:#a9dfbf;">
      🏧 كيوسك ذاتي
    </div>
    <div class="channel-body">
      <p>+20-30% متوسط الفاتورة</p>
      <p>AI Upsell • ADA متوافق</p>
      <p>دفع مدمج • قسائم</p>
      <p>Self-Service Kiosk</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 4. QR -->
  <div class="channel-card" style="border-color:#2980b9; background:#080e18;">
    <div class="channel-header" style="background:rgba(41,128,185,0.18); color:#aed6f1;">
      📱 QR منيو
    </div>
    <div class="channel-body">
      <p>PWA بلا تثبيت</p>
      <p>رقم الطاولة من الكود</p>
      <p>دفع لحظي • Qlub</p>
      <p>QR Order &amp; Pay</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 5. Talabat -->
  <div class="channel-card" style="border-color:#e67e22; background:#180e05;">
    <div class="channel-header" style="background:rgba(230,126,34,0.18); color:#f5cba7;">
      🛵 Talabat / Uber Eats
    </div>
    <div class="channel-body">
      <p>Deliverect • UrbanPiper</p>
      <p>Careem • HungerStation</p>
      <p>+15-20% channel pricing</p>
      <p>عمولة 25-35%</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 6. WhatsApp -->
  <div class="channel-card" style="border-color:#25d366; background:#050f08;">
    <div class="channel-header" style="background:rgba(37,211,102,0.15); color:#a9dfbf;">
      💬 واتساب / Chatbot
    </div>
    <div class="channel-body">
      <p>Arabot • WATI • BotR</p>
      <p>بلا عمولة • بلا تطبيق</p>
      <p>Product Catalog مباشر</p>
      <p>ربط فوري بـ POS</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</div><!-- end channels-row -->

<!-- FUNNEL CONNECTOR -->
<div class="funnel-wrap">
  <div class="funnel-line"></div>
  <div class="funnel-arrow"></div>
</div>

<!-- ═══ محرك الطلبات ═══ -->
<div class="engine-wrap">
  <div class="engine-box">
    <h3>⚡ محرك الطلبات — Order Engine / POS Core</h3>
    <div class="lifecycle">منشأ ← تحقق ← مقبول ← موجَّه ← قيد التحضير ← جاهز ← تسليم ← مدفوع ← مغلق</div>
    <div class="tags">
      <span class="etag">تحقق المخزون</span>
      <span class="etag">تطبيق المعدّلات</span>
      <span class="etag">Idempotency Key</span>
      <span class="etag">توجيه للمحطة</span>
      <span class="etag">86 Broadcast فوري</span>
      <span class="etag">مزامنة جميع القنوات</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ARROW DOWN -->
<div class="arrow-down-dashed"></div>

<!-- ═══ المطابخ الفرعية — الصف الأول ═══ -->
<div class="section-label" style="margin-top:4px;">— المطابخ الفرعية — الصف الأول —</div>
<div class="kitchen-grid">

  <!-- HOT LINE -->
  <div class="station-card st-hot">
    <div class="station-header">
      <div class="station-header-inner">
        <div class="station-title">🔥 المطبخ الحار — Hot Line</div>
        <div class="station-subtitle">صلصات • سوتيه • بروتينات مقلية • حساء</div>
      </div>
      <div class="kds-badge">📺 KDS</div>
    </div>
    <div class="prep-store">
      <div class="prep-store-header">📦 مخزن التحضير — الحار</div>
      <div class="prep-store-body">
        <div class="bom-label">وصفات نموذجية (BOM):</div>
        <div class="bom-item">برجر = خبز (80ج) + لحم مفروم (150ج) + جبن (30ج) + صلصة + خس</div>
        <div class="bom-item">باستا بولونيز = فيتوتشيني (120ج) + لحم (90ج) + صلصة طماطم (80مل)</div>
        <div class="bom-item">ريزوتو زعفران = أرز أربوريو (90ج) + مرق (220مل) + بارميزان (25ج)</div>
        <div class="bom-item">شوربة بصل = مرق (300مل) + بصل محمّر (80ج) + خبز + جبن</div>
        <div class="bom-item">دجاج بالقشطة = صدر (180ج) + قشطة (60مل) + ثوم + توابل</div>
        <div class="supply-note">↑ يستلم: مبردة + جافة + مجمدة | FIFO | خصم فوري بكل بيعة</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- GRILL -->
  <div class="station-card st-grill">
    <div class="station-header">
      <div class="station-header-inner">
        <div class="station-title">🥩 الشواء — Grill Station</div>
        <div class="station-subtitle">لحوم • شرائح • كباب • دجاج مشوي</div>
      </div>
      <div class="kds-badge">📺 KDS</div>
    </div>
    <div class="prep-store">
      <div class="prep-store-header">📦 مخزن التحضير — الشواء</div>
      <div class="prep-store-body">
